Enjoy your wizard, decide for yourself.<br>
And above all, be sure and avoid this dreaded monster...<br>
<br>
&quot;A habitual whiner&quot;<br>
<br>
There are plenty around, they give lousy experience and I've yet to see one drop any useful loot.<br>
<br>
:chuckles<br>
<br>
<br>
Happy Gaming,<br>
Orv <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukordesh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kordesh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/23/01 3:24:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ..</span><hr size=1> Nice sig Ethenil. I went to the sight that had it but coulden't figure out how to set up the things to use in a sig. Had a cool idea for one of the space ones if I could use a custome background /= <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/useverinewolfe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Severine Wolfe</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/23/01 5:34:34 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.clan-donald.com/screenshots/severine.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ..</span><hr size=1> I love my wizard to the point that my alts languish in hopes that I go on a planes raid and have to camp out.<br>
<br>
It's hard.  I won't lie to you, it is hard.  But, it is sooooo worth it.  We have a hard time at the beginning with the promise of true power in the end game.  I still remember the first time I cast Conflagration and was in awe of the power that I now beheld.  I can still remember the first time I successfully researched a spell.  I can also remember killing my first orc at level 2.<br>
<br>
